      "position": 6,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-check-square-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Click through the animated slide to introduce the steps students will take on Day 1.",
        "tips": [
          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "As you go through each bullet, preview where students can find this section in the guide and check for understanding."
